s/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇話唔比你吹奏喎，你要吹咪吹囉，踩其他黎吹唔係唔得，低莊d咁解姐<br />\n仲要FF文科先應該係本傳，接受現實啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋唔洗扣高帽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我係文乃粉<br />\n完左黑肉線就當成套野完左<br />\n唔想睇到自己鐘意嘅角色咁樣比作者拎黎糟塌救人氣咁解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T09:15:21.000Z","msg":"唔好玩啦 咁都叫引戰 <br />\n唔好怪我坦白咁講 你係咪過份解讀左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我好認真咁覺得<br />\n<br />\n我係引戰就直接拋老師出黎笑佢賣肉369冇內涵啦ching<br />\n究竟係你蠢定係我引戰<br />\n<br />\n救乜鬼人氣 全世界都知老師no.1 <br />\n我地文乃fan boy見到有啖糖食就覺得happy<br />\n唔係個個都受 好正常<br />\n話我引戰 我真係得啖笑<br />\n你同大陸仔郁d嗌辱華有咩分別<br />\n我已經冇講好難聽既說話<br />\n純覺得其他線唔好睇咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再詳細話你聽咩叫唔好睇 係悶啊<br />\n九唔撚搭八<br />\n今日我袋錢入你袋 係呢到比我笑就好啦<br />\n出到去比人笑就失禮啦"},{"pid":"d6ecb6aa2360cf8e7f60fc044c9a5e07b2ed2cd2","tid":2063560,"uid":227815,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d993bc4ad8cc0fffcbc6f33b25107a7887582528","tid":2063560,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09eba87f7e2c8ba5e6c6c71aff74cec492e775b5","tid":2063560,"uid":227815,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"4848f2225fec985dfdfd9cb48f77a13cf0ddf670","tid":2063560,"uid":6327,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T08:50:48.000Z","msg":"屎唔屎唔關我事 都冇人想知你覺得屎唔屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我眼中只有好睇唔好睇<br />\n以前係唔好睇 我就鬧<br />\n依家好睇 我吹奏下有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲叫人唔好吹一踩一咁持平<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm